<div class="">
<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/we-need-a-new-declaration-of-rights-for-black-americans/">We Need a New Declaration of Rights for Black Americans</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">The lived reality of Black Americans belies the privileges and immunities granted by the U.S. Constitution.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/taru-taylor/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Taru Taylor</a></span>, </dd>
<dd class="source org" itemprop="sourceOrganization" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Organization"><span itemprop="name"><a href='https://truthout.org' itemprop='url'>Truthout</a></span></dd>
</dl>
