<div class="">
<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/the-senate-is-an-institutional-barrier-to-democracy/">The Senate Is an Institutional Barrier to Democracy</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">Republicans have won Senate majority in 6 of the last 10 elections without representing a majority of the public.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/sohale-a-mortazavi/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Sohale A. Mortazavi</a></span>, </dd>
